<ab facs="#facs_8_r2l4">bracht <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Alſo <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅch <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fleıſʒıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> daʒ Jr darcʒu hılfflıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_8_r2l5">vnd <expan>furderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> wellet ſein daʒ den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒu <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> noch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_8_r2l6">rechts <expan>geholff<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd geſtatt vnd des ein rechttag geſecʒt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . ſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_8_r2l7">ſıe Jm mıt recht <expan>nachkome<ex>n</ex></expan> wan auch dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> . daʒ er Jr <expan>recht<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
